{"tid":535432,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖]日本係咪唯一一個女演員封胸先上到位既國家?","createTime":"2018-01-20T21:54:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-23T19:19:54.000Z","uid":67294,"like":322,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"b1b538dcd8c027c0b04de22a85a61d922af388b0","tid":535432,"uid":67294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T21:54:01.000Z","msg":"標題可能講得唔好, 意思係依家好多走紅既女優其實都有啲波路<br />\n但拍親劇或者上電視做宣傳一定著得勁密實, 唔係有寫真都唔知咁大波<br />\n<br />\n經典, 最受歡迎既女優 綾瀨遙<br />\n寫真<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.tpwang.net/image/%E7%B6%BE/artist-%E7%B6%BE%E7%80%A8%E9%81%99/%E7%B6%BE%E7%80%A8%E9%81%9964108.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.tpwang.net%2Fimage%2F%25E7%25B6%25BE%2Fartist-%25E7%25B6%25BE%25E7%2580%25A8%25E9%2581%2599%2F%25E7%25B6%25BE%25E7%2580%25A8%25E9%2581%259964108.jpg&h=ba03785e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日劇, 包到勁實<br />\n<img src=\"http://i0.sinaimg.cn/ent/s/j/2011-08-15/U5199P28T3D3386964F326DT20110815135829.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi0.sinaimg.cn%2Fent%2Fs%2Fj%2F2011-08-15%2FU5199P28T3D3386964F326DT20110815135829.jpg&h=6e4d50c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/silvery1208/1308750254-9e0ecf5e94ddd61a779af38b4ce1f1ad_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fsilvery1208%2F1308750254-9e0ecf5e94ddd61a779af38b4ce1f1ad_n.jpg&h=90cb26f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上戶彩<br />\n寫真<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/cgnWKNP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FcgnWKNP.jpg&h=a5d2966b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日劇, 本身太大唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://resource.holyshare.com.tw/uploads/article/600x0/1432631868_q1_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fresource.holyshare.com.tw%2Fuploads%2Farticle%2F600x0%2F1432631868_q1_1.jpg&h=57037616&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n長澤雅美<br />\n寫真<br />\n<